{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-requestProgress"},{"text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference"},{"text":"s about this pack that come from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"default notification center.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"progress","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier